## Getting started

##Required setup
###IDE: 
* Visual studio 2013 or MonoDevelop targeting Microsoft .NET Framework 4.5.1

###Libraries: 
* ADAPT - http://www.nuget.org/packages/AgGatewayADAPTFramework/
* ADM Plugin - http://www.nuget.org/packages/AgGatewayADMPlugin/
* ISO Plugin - http://www.nuget.org/packages/AgGatewayISOPlugin/
